=>Check TimeZone
timedatectl

=>Change TimeZone
sudo timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Dhaka

=>Check Hostname
hostname

=>Change Hostname
sudo hostname NewHostName 
OR
sudo hostnamectl set-hostname NewHostName
OR
sudo nano /etc/hostname 
after that write new hostname and save it , then write command
sudo nano /etc/hosts 
thne reboot server using ( sudo reboot) this command

=>Update All Packeg 
sudo apt-get update

=>clear screen
ctrl+L

=>current directory check
pwd

=>All of the contet/file list show with including hidden file
ls -al

=>All of hidden content/file check
ls -a

=> Make new directory
mkdir DirectoryName
or sudo mkdir DirectoryName (if permission denied)

=>Change Directory
cd directoryName
cd ~ (move to parent folder)
cd.. (back to previous directory)

=>Create File command
touch fileName 
then check using (ls command)

=>Open editor for write something's 
sudo nano editor
After that write something and save it

=>file content check
cat fileName
or sudo cat FileName (if permission denied )

=> Remove file
rm FileName 
and check ls command, It will be removed 

